## Prevention
[load_niche_rules(niche, lang)](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/tts_cleanup.py#69-78) ensures future niches automatically support multi-language — just add an [es/](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/.gitattributes) version.
